sourcesContent: import carImg from "../../images/car-winter.svg"; import React from "react"; import { Button } from "../ButtonElement"; import { InfoContainer, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Column1, Column2, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, Subtitle, BtnWrap, ImgWrap, Img, } from "./infoElements"; const InfoSection = ({ lightBg, id, imgStart, topLine, lightText, headLine, darkText, description, buttonLabel, img, alt, }) => { return ( <> {topLine} {headLine} {description} ); }; export default InfoSection;
